3)  program to check given email id and phno are valid or not.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
n=input('Enter Email Id')
k=input('Enter phone number')
c=0
flag=0
f=int(k[0])
for i in k:
    if i.isdigit():
        c=c+1
if c==10:
    flag=1
if n.endswith("@gmail.com") or n.endswith("@yahoo.com") or n.endswith("@adc.aditya.ac.in") and f>5 and flag==1:
    print("Registration successfull")
else:
    print("Check your details")
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Output:
Enter Email Idclsmeghana@yahoo.com
Enter phone number987654321
Registration successfull
